eapon File 94\",\"blockType\":\"file\"},{\"id\":\"6760a0064e864a2dff254f81\",\"title\":\"Tiv Notes 47\",\"image\":{\"id\":635,\"alt\":\"Tiv Notes File notes 47\",\"prefix\":\"media\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-12-16T22:09:38.431Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-16T22:09:38.431Z\",\"url\":\"https://lagosmuseumarchives.ng/api/media/file/Tiv%20Notes%20File%20notes%2047\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"Tiv Notes File notes 47\",\"mimeType\":\"image/jpeg\",\"filesize\":216911,\"width\":2216,\"height\":3268,\"focalX\":50,\"focalY\":50,\"sizes\":{\"thumb\":{\"url\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null,\"mimeType\":null,\"filesize\":null,\"filename\":null}}},\"description\":\"The file consists of information on Basket weaving and mat making, one of which household involved in the art is Achaia house at Gboko, etc\",\"creation\":\"1959\",\"accession\":\"1959\",\"file\":{\"id\":632,\"alt\":\"Tiv Notes File notes 47.pdf\",\"prefix\":\"media\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-12-16T21:49:19.274Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-16T21:49:19.274Z\",\"url\":\"https://lagosmuseumarchives.ng/api/media/file/Tiv%20Notes%20File%20notes%2047.pdf\",\"thumbnailURL\":null,\"filename\":\"Tiv Notes File notes 47.pdf\",\"mimeType\":\"application/pdf\",\"filesize\":31923686,\"width\":null,\"height\":null,\"focalX\":null,\"focalY\":null,\"sizes\":{\"thumb\":{\"url\":null,\"width\":null,\"height\":null,\"mimeType\":null,\"filesize\":null,\"filename\":null}}},\"authors\":\"Ikpa Ichoul\",\"keyword\":\"Mat weaving, Basket weaving, Bag\",\"condition\":\"Fair\",\"location\":\"National Musem Lagos\",\"rights\":null,\"identifiers\":\"Tiv Notes 47\",\"provenance\":\"Gboko\",\"slug\":null,\"blockName\":\"Tiv Notes 47\",\"blockType\":\"file\"},{\"id\":\"67727b3c36e75c07fc78b3fb\",\"title\":\"Archaeology of Sokoto\",\"image\":{\"id\":701,\"alt\":\"Archaeology of Sokoto\",\"prefix\":\"media\",\"updatedAt\":\"2024-12-30T10:52:18.729Z\",\"createdAt\":\"2024-12-30T10:52:18.729Z\",\"url\":\"https://lagosmuseumarchives.ng/api/media/file/